	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does he think anything other than a Vectrex or contemporary vectorscope-using arcade machines counts as vector graphics? 'Cuz I don't see a point in trying to persuade him if his definition is that strict.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
