	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Neo Geo AES and Neo Geo MVS cartridges have one PRG board and one CHR board in the same way that NES cartridge boards have a PRG half and a CHR half. The Neo Geo CD has VRAM, but no existing Neo Geo cartridge release uses a circuit like that which I described.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


